articles.title: Kim Kardashian Says She's Happy with Pete Davidson - TMZ
articles.description: Kim Kardashian says she's happy in her relationship with Pete Davidson on 'Good Morning America'.
articles.content: Kim Kardashian's done playing it cool in public when it comes to Pete Davidson ... instead, she's pouring her heart out about how happy she is, and all that's left is for one of 'em to say the L-word… [+895 chars]
